OL,3,CHeadteacher calls for complete ban on
OL,4,Csmartphones for under-16s
OL,6,FThe headteacher of a school in is
OL,7,Furging the island's government to
OL,8,Fcompletely ban under-16s from using
OL,9,Fand buying smartphones.
OL,11,FIt follows a push in the UK towards
OL,12,Fphone-free learning environments.
OL,14,FLadies' College currently has a phone
OL,15,Fban in the school building but
OL,16,FPrincipal Daniele Harford-Fox wants
OL,17,Fthis to be extended.
