OL,6,FShe explains: "My concern is that we
OL,7,Fcan see growing evidence of a massive
OL,8,Frise in mental health challenges in
OL,9,Fyoung people and that correlates
OL,10,Fexactly with the invention of the
OL,11,Fsmartphone.
OL,13,F"My worry is that the technology that
OL,14,Fwe are using is actually shaping
OL,15,Fchildren's brains differently and
OL,16,Ftherefore leading to some of the
OL,17,Freally negative outcomes."
